reviews.review_text: Mayor Phil of Bombsville Great sounding FOB, and an auspicious start to a new era in Grateful Dead history. Something tells me they got a little rain this afternoon but it clearly didn’t dampen the mood or the festivities.  Very good show overall, my only criticism would be Bob’s godawful slide, ouch.
